# v0.1.2

**New features**

- New hook: inventory relief via collectable turn-in and scrip purchases

**Improvements**

- Travel system:
  - Now supports Dravanian Hinterlands
- Combat rotations: all combat jobs now have a basic combat rotation that is tuned for bursts rather than doing an opener.
- Orchestration now automatically assigns combat grinding tasks for certain material
- Orchestration now has a try-to-unstuck routine when it detects anomalies

**Infrastructure**

*Note: these additions set up the foundation for future work, but not all features have been implemented.*

- Hooks: small tasks that run within an orchestration plan, like scrip purchasing and repairs
- Travel system: infrastructure for multi-zone traveling, airships, ferries, and housing
- Retainer inventory: infrastructure for smart retrieval from retainer inventory for undercutting and material retrieval

**In progress**

- Hook migrations to new hook system.
- Cosmic exploration.

**Fixes**

- Gathering scrip grinding is now treated as a composite timed task.
- Retainer inventory threading issues fixed
- Gathering scrip grinding now detects nodes from visible range instead of surveying spots one by one.
- Kill Rust solver threads when Drakos is undetected.
- Combat now double weaves as intended.
- Gathering scrip grind solver no longer runs on main thread.

# v0.1.1

**New features**

- Overworld combat farming
- Chocobo companion usage
- v1 avoidance of A/S-ranks and boss FATEs during overworld farming
- Configurable crafter scrip source selection
- Icebrand: ephemeral solver.

**Improvements**

- Firebrand-fast: <50ms, ~6% average distortion ~23% 95th percentile distortion
- Firebrand-mid: <500ms, ~2% average distortion ~8% 95th percentile distortion
- Firebrand-long: 10 seconds, <0.1% average distortion.
- Icebrand: No longer spends all GP on a single ephemeral node. Instead, it maps out allocates optimal GP across nodes, cordial-aware.
- Solvers migrated to Rust-FFI for more robustness.

**In progress**

- Cosmic Exploration (work has begun)

**Bug fixes**

- Fix multi-zone gathering double teleport on crystals
- Fix territory filter for multi-zone gathering items
- Fix GP allocation for normal gather nodes suppressing crystal fallback
- Fix ledger clamping causing intermediate overproduction on re-expansion
- Fix quick synth robustness
- Robustness on crafting detection due to gearset switch animation lock
- Added more stabilization delay for RecipeNote closing
- Fix GUI heartbeat killing idle external GUI connections
- Rerouted heavy scheduler logic to background threads
- Fix /drakos kill not immediately killing active solvers
- Fix stale system.status updates
- Major refactors
